      <title>大型连锁酒店和无品牌酒店业主发现他们彼此需要</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/big-hotel-chains-unbranded-hotel-owners-find-they-need-each-other-2024-03-25/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于高利率打击了酒店业，减缓了新酒店的建设速度，独立酒店运营商和大型全球连锁酒店越来越多地通过特许经营协议进行合作。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/big-hotel-chains-unbranded-hotel-owners-find-they-need-each-other-2024-03-25/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Mar 2024 05:03:16 GMT</pubDate>
